title: Running With Arnold
description:
A documentary following Arnold Schwarzenegger's whirlwind transformation from action hero to governor of California. His ambition for fame and power resulted in his winning a political circus special recall election campaign to become the leader of the world's fifth largest economy as Governor of California. With movements afoot to amend the US constitution to allow for foreign born presidential candidates how far will Arnold go in his drive for power? Will the governor's office be enough?
